column8: Their comment: Since there was no detailed instructions; I did two measurements (5 deg/min and 10 deg/min heating rates) under the dynamic nitrogen stream (50 ml/min). Measurements were performed on a TA instrument (DSC25) using standard type of TA aluminium crucibles (pan+lid)
Enthalpy reported in the collected document from the Paris drive but can't see in the paper itself. Assume its calculated wrongly
